{"name":"Dropdown-angular","tagline":"Simple dropdown directive for angular","body":"### Dropdown-angular demo\r\n\r\nSimple case:\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<div ya-dropdown='open'>\r\n    I am simple one level dropdown\r\n    <button ng-click='open = !open'>click me</button>\r\n    <div ng-if='open' ng-click='$event.stopPropagation()'>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li>First item</li>\r\n            <li>Second item</li>\r\n            <li>Third item</li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n```\r\n\r\nNested dropdowns:\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<div ya-dropdown='openParent'>\r\n    I am nested dropdown\r\n    <button ng-click='openParent = !openParent'>click me</button>\r\n    <div ng-if='openParent' ng-click='$event.stopPropagation()'>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li>First item</li>\r\n            <li>Second item</li>\r\n            <li>\r\n                <div ya-dropdown='openNested'>\r\n                    I am inner dropdown\r\n                    <button ng-click='openNested = !openNested'>click me</button>\r\n                    <div ng-if='openNested' ng-click='$event.stopPropagation()'>\r\n                        <ul>\r\n                            <li>First item</li>\r\n                            <li>Second item</li>\r\n                            <li>Third item</li>\r\n                        </ul>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n```","google":"","note":"Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration."}